{"tid":2390634,"cid":38,"subCid":0,"title":"A message from Myanmar citizens","createTime":"2021-02-01T16:12:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-01T16:25:09.000Z","uid":73381,"like":8,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"afd461eb769ca616c6c8941b6231ab3ee0dfdbb0","tid":2390634,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T16:12:34.000Z","msg":"We , Myanmar citizens need  the world to know what's happening in Myanmar right now   before our wifis are cut off. <br />\n<br />\nThey already cut off TVs broadcasting lines, phone services in order to prevent us reaching  to the world.<br />\n<br />\nAgain in 2021! History is about to be repeated like in 1988. We couldn't let it happen again,guys, please help us in spreading what's happening in Myanmar 🙏🏻🇲🇲<br />\n<br />\nHelp us.<br />\nMilitary has detained our elected democratic government,party leaders and political activists in Myanmar.Now,national television channels and phone services are cut out nationwide.<br />\nHelp us,world leading democracy #helpus<br />\n<br />\n#SaveMyanmar<br />\n<br />\n#Save #Myanmar 🇲🇲 <br />\n#Save #Burma 🇲🇲 <br />\n#We #need #democracy!!!<br />\n#Help #us #and #support #our #Leader,  #Aung #San #Suu #Kyi #government!!!<br />\n#crd"},{"pid":"55b8d1ac36f832ddd9e931dcab5dcf4e92078f3c","tid":2390634,"uid":261505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T16:16:34.000Z","msg":"換左昂山素gay都只係另一個暴政<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"746e86d07e58b93d7461509205287be0f0c4116f","tid":2390634,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"55b8d1ac36f832ddd9e931dcab5dcf4e92078f3c","tid":2390634,"uid":261505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T16:16:34.000Z","msg":"換左昂山素gay都只係另一個暴政<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T16:17:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Snx5oG5.png\" data-thumbnail-src